  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (Minimal profile)",
  "description": "This model has been applied in clinical research contexts to predict hemolysis in centrifugal blood pumps under ventricular assist device operating conditions. The CFD hemolysis model targets the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry and evaluates absolute hemolysis index predictions at Model Risk Level 5. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification was performed across all 13 ASME V&V 40 credibility factors; seven factors were formally assessed and six were flagged as epistemic gaps. All assessed factors achieved required credibility levels under the Minimal profile review. The assessment supports regulatory submission planning for a Class III VAD device. Intended use scope is described narratively in the assessment documentation rather than in a structured context record.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/vad-hemolysis-mrl5-req",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/vad-hemolysis-cfd-credibility",
  "bindsModel": "https://uofa.net/synth/model/cfd-hemolysis-fda-centrifugal-pump",
